                     <interp inst="t18131027-22-person272" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. These things I found at different parts of the prisoner's lodging. He confessed it was his masters property. In his tea chest I found some nutmegs, and ten one-pound notes.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18131027-22-person273">
                  WILLIAM 
                  ELDRIDGE
