                     <interp inst="t18131027-22-person273" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was with Harrison. I heard the prisoner say all these articles were his master's property. He said he received the ten one-pound notes for his master's goods.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I did not own to them things. Some of them were given to me by the warehouse-man. The sponge I had in particular before I ever knew Mr. Cannan.</p>
